  <metadata>
    <name>INN-L3 — Zillertal &amp; Grossglockner Chain Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from INN and ride into the Zillertal &amp; Grossglockner Chain. Hit Gerlos Pass — 1507m and Mittersill. Loop back to INN over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
